name: 777,000 miles
description: This piece was inspired by a photo taken by the Cassini spacecraft in 2017. 777,000 miles above Saturn. It's not the most stunning photo of Saturn captured on this mission but the unique vantage point really struck a chord with me. The original photo can be seen here - https://solarsystem.nasa.gov/resources/17716/haze-on-the-horizon/ // Digitally painted in Photoshop by du5t - 2019 // 3840 x 2160px // Twitter - @du5t / IG - @du5t.art
